==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Wone
<hw>Wone</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. See <er>Wone</er>, <pos>v.
i.</pos>, <er>Wont</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety>⟦br⟧
